### Hadith 4:152

*Narrated Sahl:*

When the helmet of the Prophet was smashed on his head and blood covered
his face and one of his front teeth got broken, 'Ali brought the water
in his shield and Fatima the Prophet's daughter) washed him. But when
she saw that the bleeding increased more by the water, she took a mat,
burnt it, and placed the ashes on the wound of the Prophet and so the
blood stopped oozing out.

